556
00:36:05,499 --> 00:36:08,126
Like a presence lurking
at the back of my mind.

557
00:36:08,252 --> 00:36:10,003
And I didn't like it.

558
00:36:23,517 --> 00:36:25,811
You don't have a kid, do you?

559
00:36:27,145 --> 00:36:28,021
What?

560
00:36:28,105 --> 00:36:30,399
You don't have a kid, do you?

561
00:36:30,482 --> 00:36:32,526
Of course I do! What are you on about?

562
00:36:32,609 --> 00:36:33,694
No, you don't.

563
00:36:33,777 --> 00:36:37,030
I've been watching you,
and you don't have a kid.

564
00:36:38,532 --> 00:36:41,493
What is it to you, anyway?
Nothing.

565
00:36:41,743 --> 00:36:45,914
