567
00:36:48,250 --> 00:36:49,376
Why?

568
00:36:49,459 --> 00:36:50,460
'Cause I'm busy.

569
00:36:50,711 --> 00:36:54,840
- What are you doing?
- I'm watching TV.

570
00:36:55,757 --> 00:36:58,135
I could watch it with you, if you like.

571
00:36:58,260 --> 00:36:59,595
That's very nice of you...

572
