575
00:37:09,271 --> 00:37:11,481
I meant, why don't you go home
and do your homework?

576
00:37:11,565 --> 00:37:13,150
I'll do you a deal.

577
00:37:13,192 --> 00:37:17,487
I won't tell anyone you don't have a kid
if you go out with my mum.

578
00:37:21,700 --> 00:37:24,161
You'd want your mum
to go out with someone like me?

579
00:37:24,286 --> 00:37:25,704
You're not too bad.

580
00:37:25,787 --> 00:37:28,999
I mean, you told lies,
but apart from that you seem okay.

