00:39:40,923 --> 00:39:43,842
Hello, everybody.
Welcome to the game of Countdown.

596
00:39:43,926 --> 00:39:47,095
You remember yesterday, Carol,
I revealed to a grateful nation...

597
00:39:47,179 --> 00:39:49,014
that our guest, Tom O'Connell...

598
00:39:49,097 --> 00:39:52,059
Yes.
He, like all of us, changes for each show.

599
00:39:52,142 --> 00:39:53,519
But he is such a...

