They've got these funny strappy things.

692
00:46:33,460 --> 00:46:34,711
It's called Velcro.

693
00:46:34,795 --> 00:46:37,214
It's a revolutionary new technology.

694
00:46:39,925 --> 00:46:43,053
For Christ's sake. It's not hard.

695
00:46:45,389 --> 00:46:47,349
All right, wait a minute, it is a bit hard.

696
00:46:47,474 --> 00:46:50,394
- Everything all right?
- Yeah, thanks.

697
00:46:51,812 --> 00:46:54,606
Pretty trendy, your old man, isn't he?

698
00:46:58,110 --> 00:47:00,153
There. You think you look cool, don't you?

699
00:47:00,237 --> 00:47:01,405
Don't know.

700
00:47:01,613 --> 00:47:05,450
- Do you think I look cool?
- Yeah, Marcus.

701
00:47:06,493 --> 00:47:09,329
- I think you look cool.
- Yeah.

702
00:47:11,957 --> 00:47:15,210
That's it, you got the walk.
That's really cool.

703
00:47:16,753 --> 00:47:19,965
Brilliant. High five. Yeah.

704
00:47:20,382 --> 00:47:23,552
I was suddenly hit by an extraordinary
rush of well-being.

705
00:47:23,635 --> 00:47:26,471
So this is what people
meant by a natural high.

706
00:47:26,555 --> 00:47:28,807
